                    <tr class="text-center align-middle">
                        <th scope="row" class="display-5">Ramona Flowers</th>
                        <td>Ramona Flowers is the love interest of Scott Pilgrim. Just like Scott Pilgrim, she also has her faults and she is more of the "indie grunge" type who is very mysterious. She has many unclosed relationships called the "seven evil exes". In which those people are the ones who were a victim to her actions due to her unhealthy habit of leaving no proper closure in her relationships. Scott Pilgrim and Ramona Flowers are both the protagonist of the story but they are not the heroes but they are two people resolving and learning from their mistakes.</td>
                        <td><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/80/28/fb/8028fb4e2d5d6909c9d8406dab5d9761.jpg" alt="Kuroo body picture" width="250" height="250" class="rounded-circle mx-auto d-block"></td>
