                        <th scope="row" class="display-5">Roxxy Richter</th>
                        <td>Roxxy Richter is a part of the "seven evil exes" of Ramona Flowers. What makes her interesting for me is that in the series, she validates the "seven evil exes" throughout the story. She shows her hurt and that the "seven evil exes" were only people who needed closure and the amount of mental damage Ramona Flowers can do. In which helped Ramona gain self awareness and learn from her mistakes</td>
